---
import { vendors } from "../../lib/vendors";
---

<section class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
      Streamlining Identity Verification and Compliance in 2026
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
      Navigating the global regulatory landscape requires robust infrastructure.
      IT and security teams face the critical challenge of balancing seamless
      user onboarding with strict FATF, GDPR, and regional compliance mandates.
      Vendor selection has direct downstream impact on fraud rates, conversion,
      and audit exposure.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
      PrimeBiometry is an independent evaluation hub tracking {vendors.length}+
      enterprise-grade vendors across{" "}
      <a href="/categories/identity-verification" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">identity verification</a>,
      biometric liveness detection,{" "}
      <a href="/categories/kyc-compliance" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">KYC compliance</a>,{" "}
      <a href="/categories/aml" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">AML</a>,
      and fraud prevention. We publish original analysis, not republished
      marketplace summaries.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
      How We Evaluate KYC and AML Vendors
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
      Our framework filters marketplace noise to deliver objective data. Each
      vendor is scored against five weighted technical criteria:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed list-disc pl-5 marker:text-zinc-400">
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-medium">Compliance coverage (20%):</strong> SOC 2, ISO 27001, GDPR, CCPA, HIPAA, and iBeta PAD certifications.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-medium">Integration depth (25%):</strong> REST APIs, native mobile SDKs, webhooks, sandbox quality, and documentation.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-medium">Market coverage (25%):</strong> supported countries, document types, languages, and liveness detection.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-medium">Pricing transparency (15%):</strong> published tiers, per-verification rates, free tier or trial availability.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-medium">User sentiment (15%):</strong> aggregated ratings from G2, Gartner, and Capterra.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      <a href="/methodology" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">
        Read the full methodology →
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
